Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.90,0:00:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.71,0:00:19.61,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Newdays 開始的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.68,0:00:23.48,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,給世界一個吻吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.61,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Blowing in thewind
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.69,0:00:31.78,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,把一點點的勇氣和愛放進口袋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.39,0:00:40.53,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,l wish如果我有翅膀的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.60,0:00:50.20,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管悲傷、過去還是不安 都能夠飛越
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.28,0:00:51.94,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,OhYeah！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.01,0:00:58.61,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有失去什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.69,0:01:00.68,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemyway！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.75,0:01:03.55,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,想用這掌心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.62,0:01:07.22,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,抓住奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.90,0:01:16.67,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,朝向無盡的天空和大地 以及未來旅行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.74,0:01:19.87,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,剛長出的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.94,0:01:23.17,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh！ 一定一定一定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.24,0:01:24.44,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.51,0:01:28.74,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,展現光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.36,0:01:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.09,0:01:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.27,0:01:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳醒了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.54,0:01:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臉色看起來已經好多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.14,0:01:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說已經過了危險期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.01,0:01:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過妳還是稍微躺著休息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.05,0:02:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個都沒睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.35,0:02:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳這個病人\N還有餘力擔心別人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.92,0:02:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿點吃的過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.82,0:02:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得保存點體力才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.46,0:02:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#06 騎士們的迷惘之歌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.21,0:02:28.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來蟲毒大概都解了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.34,0:02:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經可以下床了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過為了以防萬一\N再吃一次那個藥草吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.02,0:02:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德伊魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.28,0:02:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的事情你已經知道了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.29,0:02:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.26,0:02:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德伊魯會辭去騎士的工作\N聽說是因為以前把廢棄公主...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.13,0:02:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.90,0:02:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是把還是嬰兒的妳\N丟到山谷底下的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.47,0:03:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒想過治好妳之後\N可以得到妳的原諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.08,0:03:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來吧，不必客氣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.78,0:03:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳大概有一大堆話想說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.75,0:03:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.59,0:03:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我改變了德伊魯的人生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.92,0:03:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.99,0:03:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向我說對不起嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.23,0:03:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向我這個想要殺妳的人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.63,0:03:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼像妳這樣的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.64,0:03:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以這麼地堅強...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.91,0:03:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當時覺得很害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.24,0:03:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的貫徹正義\N難道只是去破壞其它的正義嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.52,0:03:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天我會不會又犯下\N無法挽回的錯誤呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.42,0:03:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為害怕這樣，所以我逃走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是妳卻...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓妳擔心，我實在不敢當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.03,0:03:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過有妳這句話就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.63,0:04:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是讓背負殘酷命運的妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.77,0:04:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還要擔起我過去犯下的罪過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.04,0:04:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我可就不配當一個人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.34,0:04:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,德伊魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.21,0:04:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不必送你回去嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.28,0:04:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用走的回去就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.12,0:04:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要活下去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.99,0:04:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能說的只有這個了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.16,0:04:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.53,0:04:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一定會的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.31,0:04:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很危險耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.94,0:04:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不是因為雷歐太大意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.98,0:04:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可是沒辦法\N成為一位出色的騎士喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.99,0:04:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.39,0:04:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經完全康復了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.02,0:05:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，你一次也沒來看我\N不覺得太冷淡了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.06,0:05:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.36,0:05:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說愛我的那些話\N原來都是謊言啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.90,0:05:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你只是在玩弄我的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.94,0:05:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.04,0:05:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個...我是因為...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.14,0:05:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.01,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.08,0:05:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不光是拿藥草這件事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.55,0:05:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你一起旅行真的很快樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.59,0:05:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，一直沒跟你說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.95,0:05:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是故意要瞞著你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.96,0:05:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.81,0:05:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.08,0:05:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道，他的馬也不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.05,0:05:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.48,0:05:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次見面時最好小心點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.69,0:06:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定他會突然一劍砍過來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.85,0:06:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.36,0:06:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然發現妳是廢棄公主\N這些都是有可能發生的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.76,0:06:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐怎麼可能會這麼做呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.70,0:06:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管是誰變成敵人\N都沒什麼好奇怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.87,0:06:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨天那種事\N我可不想再發生第二次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.44,0:06:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴雷特大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.18,0:06:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.01,0:06:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道該怎麼辦才好...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.38,0:06:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果帕希菲卡\N真的是毀滅世界的災禍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為騎士的我應該要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.56,0:06:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.59,0:06:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是騎士，只是一個醫生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.23,0:06:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒辦法回答你的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.76,0:06:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在眼前的就算是壞人\N如果是醫生的話就可以去救他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.00,0:06:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使去救的那一瞬間\N有可能會被殺掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.21,0:06:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說過嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.98,0:06:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騎士的精神就是為了正義而揮劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.55,0:07:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你覺得真是這樣\N那就去砍下她的頭顱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.38,0:07:05.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最少也可以獲頒一枚勳章吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.35,0:07:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所追求的就是這一條路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.56,0:07:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主到底是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.07,0:07:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有多少人因為我受到傷害呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.58,0:07:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.28,0:07:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我妹妹還活著的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該跟我長得很像吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.65,0:07:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅世界的劇毒是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.75,0:07:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個神諭到底是什麼意思呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.66,0:07:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.53,0:07:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道她還活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.96,0:07:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妹妹大概又會被追殺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.86,0:07:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想母親也一定會很擔心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王后殿下？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.90,0:07:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我很久沒見到我母親了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.14,0:08:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在跟朋友聊天...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.21,0:08:07.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.78,0:08:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把頭抬起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.92,0:08:12.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是\N在下是克里斯多福．柏拉赫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,國王殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.62,0:08:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柏拉赫的養子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.80,0:08:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嚇到你了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟父親總是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.47,0:08:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為父親一直很討厭我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.88,0:08:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過啊，那個帶著樂器的殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.01,0:08:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕音殺手嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.55,0:08:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會再來攻擊我們呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.15,0:08:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就難說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.52,0:08:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那時候他雖然乖乖地離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.49,0:08:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別告訴我妳用什麼方法\N讓他乖乖離開的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.16,0:08:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那會讓我吃不下飯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.33,0:08:56.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是什麼人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.13,0:08:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.27,0:09:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走上前來吧，守護者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.72,0:09:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.52,0:09:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是普通人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.43,0:09:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.30,0:09:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然身為秩序守護者的我\N親自出馬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.77,0:09:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可就跟那個時候不一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.24,0:09:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.65,0:09:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怪物是這傢伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.89,0:09:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.52,0:09:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.89,0:09:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.66,0:10:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以讓這兩個人\N在這裡自相殘殺喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.40,0:10:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人類對我絕對服從
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.10,0:10:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這正是律法的應有面貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.75,0:10:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥！姊姊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.76,0:10:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！可惡！什麼正義！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼騎士精神！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.77,0:10:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.91,0:10:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉蔻兒姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.78,0:10:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.75,0:10:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐，拜託你救救...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.63,0:11:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉默是你們兩人愛的語言嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.57,0:11:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是根木頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.00,0:11:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕音殺手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.20,0:11:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀，拿那把劍對著我幹嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.17,0:11:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位小姐可是毀滅世界的劇毒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.41,0:11:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛不是打算砍那位小姐嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.01,0:11:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.28,0:11:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是絕音殺手是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.72,0:11:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔蟲可以用來找人嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.39,0:11:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.59,0:11:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要做個交易？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.80,0:11:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交易？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.96,0:11:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給你一條手臂\N這樣你就能領賞金了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.74,0:11:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.50,0:11:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說，妳給我一條手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.87,0:11:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我當作已經殺了妳\N而放妳逃走是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.44,0:11:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.61,0:11:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我說過這是一筆交易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.68,0:12:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我給你一條手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.02,0:12:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相對的你操縱魔蟲\N找出我的哥哥和姊姊在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.75,0:12:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.83,0:12:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.13,0:12:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能答應我最後的請求嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,砍斷它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.37,0:12:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.70,0:12:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快一點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.58,0:12:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏儂哥和拉蔻兒姊被抓走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.18,0:12:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到的只有這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.96,0:12:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.50,0:12:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.45,0:13:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是為了做這種事才拿劍的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.39,0:13:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的劍...所謂的劍...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.66,0:13:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是只為了打打殺殺而存在的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.03,0:13:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是不是誤會了我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.34,0:13:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別看我這樣\N我也知道什麼時候該收手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.07,0:13:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說明白點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.31,0:13:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想在傷了這位小姐之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.11,0:13:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慘遭她的哥哥姊姊尋仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.45,0:13:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可...可是這樣我就傷腦筋了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.45,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以說，不談交易條件也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.26,0:13:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少女獻出手臂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騎士奉獻生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詩人則是獻上他的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.77,0:14:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧，我的手下們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.08,0:14:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布拉寧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.94,0:14:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要在你們自傲的\N其中一個要塞裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.51,0:14:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅你們最後的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.55,0:14:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接著人類就會把\N"律法破壞者"處理掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.86,0:14:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舊世界的殘骸嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.13,0:14:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像魔蟲這種東西能做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.13,0:14:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣輕視他人\N正是你的愚蠢之處
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.81,0:14:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.41,0:14:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙會替你們帶路\N跟在牠後面去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.89,0:14:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.02,0:14:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絕音殺手大叔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.26,0:14:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？大...大叔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.43,0:15:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.10,0:15:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳侵入了魔蟲的通信網啊\N賽菲莉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.73,0:15:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有我的主人，龍騎士\N才可以用那個名字叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.97,0:15:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你這種次級品\N沒資格這樣叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.14,0:15:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳說我是次級品？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.04,0:15:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.32,0:15:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.49,0:15:31.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點到那邊去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.63,0:15:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.09,0:15:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？雷歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.63,0:15:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二級神罰執行型態
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.68,0:16:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以，不可以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.05,0:16:02.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以過去...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.06,0:16:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以反抗那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.29,0:16:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐你怎麼了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.03,0:16:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不過是個怪物而已啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.16,0:16:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.26,0:16:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以跟那個戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.23,0:16:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雷歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.11,0:16:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.07,0:16:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然妳打算在守護者當中\N選一個當新的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.71,0:16:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是他們都在我的律法控制之下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.08,0:16:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳一點勝算也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.53,0:16:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.10,0:16:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.80,0:16:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...沒辦法保護她嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.34,0:16:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等級差太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.41,0:17:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼都做不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.35,0:17:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是發過誓要保護她嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.32,0:17:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，我是發過誓...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.56,0:17:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要從所有想奪走她的人手中\N保護她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.46,0:17:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以扭轉命運的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使與全世界...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.87,0:17:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至與神為敵\N都能對抗的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.97,0:17:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的意志對吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.61,0:17:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我將服從它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是暫時的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.85,0:17:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我承認你有資格成為我的操縱者\N"龍騎士"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:39.35,0:17:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我，亞菲M4龍機神\N系列編號26，賽菲莉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.36,0:17:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將成汝之利刃，毀滅敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.65,0:18:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.65,0:18:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姊姊\N危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.95,0:18:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毀滅吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.67,0:18:26.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍機神？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.57,0:18:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.94,0:18:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為什麼會有這種力量？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.48,0:18:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保護妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.98,0:18:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要把你們分解成基本粒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.16,0:18:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牆啊，阻擋一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.44,0:19:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.08,0:19:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.33,0:19:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是某人從遙遠的時空彼方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.60,0:19:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,送給你們的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.40,0:19:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當你們產生了\N與神戰鬥的意志之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會出現來幫助你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.04,0:19:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藏在空間夾縫中的最後一頭龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.51,0:19:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與神戰鬥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.45,0:19:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不太明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.89,0:19:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在是這樣子也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是你必須記住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.49,0:20:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有完全復活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.63,0:20:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能出現在這個世界的時間\N是有限制的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.90,0:20:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我也不能介入\N人類之間的紛爭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.70,0:20:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不是萬能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.17,0:20:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是當你們要和\N剩下的三位秩序守護者作戰之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.04,0:20:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有和天神瑪烏傑魯作戰之時\N請呼喚我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.25,0:20:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼叫只有吾主才能稱呼的\N吾之真名 賽菲莉絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.52,0:20:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賽菲莉絲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.96,0:20:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到時候我會化為龍騎士\N夏儂．卡蘇魯之利刃，毀滅敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.70,0:20:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍...騎士？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.46,0:20:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我為了幫助你\N已經等候了五千年以上的時光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.04,0:20:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.44,0:20:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後會有期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.87,0:20:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我暫時的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.58,0:20:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.65,0:21:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底...是什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.92,0:21:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的廢棄公主...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.89,0:21:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算回塔爾斯鎮一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.03,0:21:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，發生這麼多事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.07,0:21:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們會感到寂寞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.40,0:21:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕希菲卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.97,0:21:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是不知道該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.41,0:21:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騎士精神這種東西\N會不會只是個無形的幻影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:25.85,0:21:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是願意相信\N有一種任何人都能相信的正義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.42,0:21:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是當我一旦找到答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.32,0:21:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我或許會變成妳的敵人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.42,0:21:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算那樣也沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後會有期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.55,0:22:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後會有期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.32,0:22:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被追殺的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.16,0:22:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與追求真理的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.73,0:22:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在此分道揚鑣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.93,0:22:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然而...然而...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.17,0:22:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我果然不適合當詩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.15,0:22:42.95,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,滋潤大地的雨水靜靜地飄下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.02,0:22:48.22,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,落在很遠很遠的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.29,0:22:55.63,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,將這愛的雨滴獻給 某個等待已久的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.70,0:23:01.30,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,清晨的微風吹過沾有雨滴的臉龐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.37,0:23:06.28,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,現在你感覺到什麼呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.35,0:23:09.71,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,這雨滴有著明白的含意 比一切都還要...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.78,0:23:14.69,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那唯一的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.75,0:23:21.32,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,停駐在追趕著的雲影下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.39,0:23:24.63,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,在這心靈的旅程中想要找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.70,0:23:28.00,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,不管到哪裡不管到哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.07,0:23:34.60,OPED,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天會再聽到熟悉的聲音
